WEBVTT

19:36.220 --> 19:37.170 line:80%
How dare you,

19:37.680 --> 19:39.240 line:80%
a scoundrel, run wild here?

19:39.350 --> 19:41.070 line:80%
I've dealt with countless men like you.

19:41.070 --> 19:41.960 line:80%
Send him back to the Wu's Mansion

19:41.960 --> 19:43.000 line:80%
and hand him over to Mrs. Wu!

19:43.000 --> 19:43.590 line:80%
Yes.

19:44.800 --> 19:45.480 line:80%
Let go!
